name: Boquet-manager
tagline: Useful Java FX application for managing XML files which are consis of sattelite channels information
body:
### Welcome to Boquet - manager a Java FX Application.
This application provide a GUI which gives you nice experience for managing of sat channels, for the following sat receiver:
Dbox2 (Neutrino)

### Authors and Contributors
Currently its only one person who works on this project me (Alexander Orlovsky) if you wish to contact me here is my email javaprofi[at]gmx.de
